{"word":"κομήτης","slug":"κομήτης","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κομήτης</b></el> <el>(κομήτης, ου,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:κομάω'><el>κομάω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>wearing long hair, long-haired</i>, <a href='S:apud (quoted in)'>ap.</a> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a>, <el>ἰὸς κ.</el> <i>a feathered</i> arrow, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>; <el>λειμὼν κ.</el> a <i>grassy</i> meadow, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>as <a href='S:Substantive'>Subst.</a> <i>a comet</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}